metadata.description:
1/ With a Diamond Pass Ticket, you will be whitelisted for a Diamond Pass.
Diamond Pass is Nswap’s utility-enabled card.

Utilities: 
1. Holder exclusive Raffles without tasks and verification
2. Future PFP project airdrop / free mint
3. Regular Raffle of hot NFT projects from secondary market
4. Preferential access rights to the platform 
5. Tokenization

2/  NFT Airdrop Raffle:
Diamond Pass Ticket holders will get a chance to win a secret NFT airdrop in Nswap’s Discord (Value > 0.2eth)
Time: June 9th - 23rd
